{"tid":660171,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台中+台南五日四夜路線，求意見","createTime":"2018-05-10T13:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T15:20:58.000Z","uid":50301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"feecddc21c037c538c0d26f02ddacc88aa19e67e","tid":660171,"uid":50301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:00:37.000Z","msg":"主意睇館/文創，第一次去冇地鐵既地方，好淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n星期三至日<br />\n<br />\nDAY1<br />\n東海大學&gt;東海藝術街商圈&gt;東海夜市<br />\nDAY2<br />\n彩虹眷村&gt;國立臺灣美術館&gt;綠光計畫范特喜文創聚落&gt;勤美誠品綠園道/勤美術館&gt;逢甲夜市<br />\nDAY3<br />\n中文化創意產業園區&gt;TO TAINAN<br />\n藍曬圖文創園區&gt;大東夜市(五)<br />\nDAY4:奇美博物館&gt;喜事集+喜事老街&gt;花園夜市(六)<br />\nDAY5<br />\n台南文化創意產業園區&gt;台南海安路藝術街&amp;神農街藝術街&gt;林百貨&gt;高雄返香港<br />\n<br />\n台中酒店係一中商圈<br />\n台南係火車站<br />\n<br />\n路線有冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef9dd30c84a31d89fcc65cdebef46ab9e27c8ff","tid":660171,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:14:44.000Z","msg":"輕輕鬆鬆鄧梓峰啦"},{"pid":"9c97c38fb6244da6b78d0bdf1005107fa2f42297","tid":660171,"uid":50301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eef9dd30c84a31d89fcc65cdebef46ab9e27c8ff","tid":660171,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:14:44.000Z","msg":"輕輕鬆鬆鄧梓峰啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:21:07.000Z","msg":"係咪冇問題可以去馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057e8c1456243a334d7500862e0372a70b3e7e8a","tid":660171,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c97c38fb6244da6b78d0bdf1005107fa2f42297","tid":660171,"uid":50301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eef9dd30c84a31d89fcc65cdebef46ab9e27c8ff","tid":660171,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:14:44.000Z","msg":"輕輕鬆鬆鄧梓峰啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14